import React, { useState } from 'react' import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom' const UpdateResturant = () => { const {id} = useParams(); const [name, setName] = useState(""); const [location, setLocation] = useState(""); const [priceRange, setPriceRange] = useState(""); return (
setName(e.target.value)} id='name' className='form-control' type='text' />
setLocation(e.target.value)} id='location' className='form-control' type='text' />
setPriceRange(e.target.value)} id='price_range' className='form-control' type='number' />
) } export default UpdateResturant
